dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2023. [This feature class contains all of the roads in Rock County, Wisconsin. They are captured as needed using GPS. The main purpose of this data is for use by 9-1-1 Communications as input into the Computer Aided Dispatch system. They do, however, fit many other purposes as used by other county departments.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
